        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued May 2 at 5:31PM EDT until May 2 at 6:00PM EDT by NWS Binghamton NY</headline>
        <description>At 531 PM EDT, a severe thunderstorm was located over Lanesboro, or
10 miles southwest of Deposit, moving east at 35 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Lakeside, Susquehanna Depot, Susquehanna, Lanesboro, Thompson,
Lakeview, and Deposit.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
